collection.description:
Bored Pixel Cats! 4554 algorithmically composed unique bored pixel cats.       

Why no properties?    
Because we believe that you should buy what you like and after that based on some numbers.    
We don't want the bots to buy the rarest ones. Everyone have a fair chance now.    
After all cats are dropped we will explain everything and add properties.

If you buy a cat then share it on Twitter, Discord...let people know about the project and this way we will grow together.

Lot of rare ones for early supporters & lot of surprises.     
 
Not affiliated with Cool Cats NFT or other cat projects.
